description: This is a market on predicting the statements made by Trump during his interview with Lex Friedman.

markets.description:
Lex Fridman, tweeted that he would be releasing an interview with Donald Trump on Tuesday Sept. 3 (see: https://x.com/lexfridman/status/1830811232502268015).

This market will resolve to "Yes" if Trump says "Comrade Kamala" during his interview with Lex Friedman currently scheduled for September 3. Otherwise, the market will resolve to "No". If no interview between Fridman and Trump is publicly released by September 6, 2024, 11:59 PM ET this market will resolve to "No".

Any usage of the word regardless of context will count toward the resolution of this market.

Pluralization/possessive of the word will count toward the resolution of this market, however other forms will NOT count.

The resolution source will be the first publicly released footage of the interview, which includes substantial and continuous content.
markets.question: Will Trump say "Comrade Kamala" during Lex interview?
